00063 void
00064 BlockCompressionCodecBmz::deflate(const DynamicBuffer &input,
00065                                   DynamicBuffer &output,
00066                                   BlockCompressionHeader &header,
00067                                   size_t reserve) {
00068   size_t inlen = input.fill();
00069   size_t headerlen = header.length();
00070   size_t outlen = bmz_pack_buflen(inlen);
00071 
00072   output.reserve(outlen + headerlen + reserve);
00073   m_workmem.reserve(bmz_pack_worklen(inlen, m_fp_len), true);
00074 
00075   HT_EXPECT(bmz_pack(input.base, inlen, output.base + headerlen, &outlen,
00076                      m_offset, m_fp_len, 0, m_workmem.base) == BMZ_E_OK,
00077             Error::BLOCK_COMPRESSOR_DEFLATE_ERROR);
00078 
00079   // in case of an incompressible block
00080   if (outlen >= inlen) {
00081     header.set_compression_type(NONE);
00082     memcpy(output.base + headerlen, input.base, inlen);
00083     header.set_data_length(inlen);
00084     header.set_data_zlength(inlen);
00085   }
00086   else {
00087     header.set_compression_type(BMZ);
00088     header.set_data_length(inlen);
00089     header.set_data_zlength(outlen);
00090   }
00091   header.set_data_checksum(fletcher32(output.base + headerlen,
00092                                       header.get_data_zlength()));
00093   output.ptr = output.base;
00094   header.encode(&output.ptr);
00095   output.ptr += header.get_data_zlength();
00096 }

00098 void
00099 BlockCompressionCodecBmz::inflate(const DynamicBuffer &input,
00100                                   DynamicBuffer &output,
00101                                   BlockCompressionHeader &header) {
00102   const uint8_t *ip = input.base;
00103   size_t remain = input.fill();
00104 
00105   header.decode(&ip, &remain);
00106   HT_EXPECT(header.get_data_zlength() == remain,
00107             Error::BLOCK_COMPRESSOR_BAD_HEADER);
00108   HT_EXPECT(header.get_data_checksum() == fletcher32(ip, remain),
00109             Error::BLOCK_COMPRESSOR_CHECKSUM_MISMATCH);
00110 
00111   size_t outlen = header.get_data_length();
00112 
00113   if (header.get_compression_type() == NONE)
00114     memcpy(output.base, ip, outlen);
00115   else {
00116     output.reserve(outlen);
00117     m_workmem.reserve(bmz_unpack_worklen(outlen), true);
00118 
00119     HT_EXPECT(bmz_unpack(ip, header.get_data_zlength(), output.base, &outlen,
00120                          m_workmem.base) == BMZ_E_OK,
00121               Error::BLOCK_COMPRESSOR_INFLATE_ERROR);
00122     HT_EXPECT(outlen == header.get_data_length(),
00123               Error::BLOCK_COMPRESSOR_INFLATE_ERROR);
00124   }
00125   output.ptr = output.base + outlen;
00126 }
